Don't you dare fight.

52
00:03:45,930 --> 00:03:46,940
Why not?

53
00:03:46,940 --> 00:03:50,610
Idiot! Whether you attack or get struck,

54
00:03:50,610 --> 00:03:54,100
Nami-san will feel the whole impact too!

55
